about.summary: Provides high performance container data types such as Queue, Stack, Deque, Dict and OrderedDict. Benchmarks <https://randy3k.github.io/collections/articles/benchmark.html> have shown that these containers are asymptotically more efficient than those offered by other packages.

name: r-collections
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = '0.2.0' %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-collections
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/collections_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/collections/collections_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 7145ad84aa614ff39d0651d2b48d457f1cfeab71c9cb8a52ac513b49c5773613

build:
  merge_build_host: True  # [win]
  number: 0
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}              # [not win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_c') }}        # [win]
    - {{posix}}filesystem        # [win]
    - {{posix}}make
    - {{posix}}sed               # [win]
    - {{posix}}coreutils         # [win]
    - {{posix}}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-xptr
  run:
    - r-base
    - {{native}}gcc-libs         # [win]
    - r-xptr

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('collections')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('collections')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://randy3k.github.io/collections
  license: MIT
  summary: Provides high performance container data types such as Queue, Stack, Deque, Dict and
    OrderedDict. Benchmarks <https://randy3k.github.io/collections/articles/benchmark.html>
    have shown that these containers are asymptotically more efficient than those offered
    by other packages.
  license_family: MIT
  license_file:
    - '{{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/MIT'
    - LICENSE

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
